    "body": "Here's a simple unit test:\n\n``` python\nimport pandas as pd\nfrom pandas.util.testing import assert_series_equal, assert_frame_equal\ndef test_groupby_syntactic_sugar():\n    df = pd.DataFrame(dict(key1=[0]*3+[1]*3, data1=range(6), data2=range(3)*2))\n    expected = df['data1'].groupby(df['key1']).count()\n    actual = df.groupby('key1')['data1'].count()\n    assert_series_equal(expected, actual)\n    expected_df = df[['data2']].groupby(df['key1']).count()\n    actual_df = df.groupby('key1')[['data2']].count()\n    assert_frame_equal(expected_df, actual_df)\n\ntest_groupby_syntactic_sugar()\n```\n"
